  <steps>
    <Step id="0c325a8e-69d1-4148-8fa3-4b4ffd3dced4" name="Soil Disturbance Classes" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;Each soil disturbance class has easily identifiable indicators that are important to become familiar with as you conduct your soil assessment and monitoring. The Soil Disturbance Field Guide  has 7 chapters that provided detailed descriptions and photographic examples-over a wide range of climatic and vegetative conditions-of the undisturbed soil condition and three soil-disturbance classes. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Chapter 1 Introduction to Visual Soil-Disturbance Classes.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Chapter 2 Soil-Disturbance-Class Attributes.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Chapter 3 Defines Class 0 - Undisturbed.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Chapter 4 Defines Soil-Disturbance Class 1.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Chapter 5 Defines Soil-Disturbance Class 2.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Chapter 6 Defines Soil-Disturbance Class 3.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Chapter 7 Mechanized Equipment Used. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" intro="true">
